 {"id":"bd-mblr.5.3.2","title":"Migrate existing E2E logs to unified schema","description":"Refactor existing log emission points to conform to the schema and remove drift across runners/tests. Output: schema-compliant event stream across entrypoints.","design":"Perform migration by event family, with contract tests per family to catch field regressions immediately.","acceptance_criteria":"- Existing emitters are migrated to schema-compliant event shapes with no ambiguous legacy fields.
- Migration includes translation layer or one-time refactor plan with explicit deprecation timeline.
- Backfill verification confirms representative historical flows still produce analyzable logs.","notes":"Prefer direct refactor over long-lived compatibility shims unless strictly necessary. This migration explicitly depends on scenario traceability mapping so emitted events and scenario IDs stay coherent.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:07.613347294Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T00:43:36.743892879Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.3.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.4.1.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-13T00:42:22.582124217Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.3.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.5.3","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:07.613347294Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.3.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.5.3.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:36.137586466Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-mblr.5.4","title":"Log Quality Validation Tests and Runbook","description":"Add automated checks that validate log completeness, schema compliance, and correlation consistency; publish a runbook showing how to trace a failure from summary output to raw event sequence.","design":"Combine contract/golden tests with semantic validators (required context around failures, correlation continuity, etc.).","acceptance_criteria":"- Automated tests verify schema compliance, field completeness, ordering/correlation consistency, and diagnostic richness.
- Runbook shows end-to-end failure triage path from CI summary to raw event sequence and artifacts.
- Log quality gate criteria are explicit and enforceable in CI.","notes":"Quality checks should prevent both silent field loss and low-signal logs that are technically valid but operationally useless.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:24:36.205409504Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T00:05:49.196374538Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.4","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.5","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:24:36.205409504Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.4","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.5.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:25:12.045699130Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.4","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.5.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:25:12.300146998Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-mblr.5.4.1","title":"Golden tests for log quality and field completeness","description":"Add tests validating required fields, event ordering expectations, and error-context richness in emitted logs. Output: stable golden or contract tests guarding log regressions.","design":"Use fixture-driven event streams and schema validators with explicit per-field assertions for critical events.","acceptance_criteria":"- Golden/contract tests fail on missing required fields, invalid value types, broken correlations, or weak failure context.
- Tests cover success and failure flows across runner entrypoints.
- Test output pinpoints exact field/path violations to reduce debugging time.","notes":"These tests should validate schema/field quality together with artifact-link integrity, so they intentionally depend on failure bundle schema completion (bd-mblr.4.4.1).","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:07.883351703Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T00:10:21.725794219Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.4.1","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.4.4.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-13T00:10:21.653062884Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.4.1","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.5.1.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:37.216534191Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.4.1","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.5.2.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:37.464549528Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.4.1","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.5.3.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:36.891330136Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.5.4.1","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.5.4","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:07.883351703Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
